Tuesday, August 23, 1994

MOTION DOCKET

94-1553. State ex rel. Governor v. Taft.

In Mandamus and Prohibition. On written request of counsel for respondent, it is ordered that the time for filing merit brief is hereby extended to September 2, 1994.

Resnick and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., dissent.
